        customerIdentifier.setCountry(country);
    }
}

return customerSummary;
```

## Style mistake #2: stringly typing

Why isn&#39;t the refType field in `CustomerIdentifier` just `RefType`? Why are you converting RefType instances to strings and back?

DB engines support enums and if they don&#39;t, the in-between layer (your DTO) should support marshalling enums into strings and back.

